name: Petals
description: Going forward in history, the colonial line takes us to Colonial Brazil, where the Portuguese influence set the rules for society. "Petals" has this inspiration.  The image posted here is a 3D simulation of the art in a frame (the floor and wall are also 3D render).  After purchasing you'll get the high resolution digital file (.ai) It is also a unit from a repeat, this means it can be placed sideways in all directions repeatedly, creating an infinite pattern.
